CustomField.description: This field is optional. It is the net, externally-calculated dollar amount of federal withholding to print on the distribution or election form, including the standard 10%, as applicable, applied to the distribution subtotal, plus any discretionary additional dollar amount or percentage.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The net dollar amount of Federal Withholding, including the standard 10% applied to the distribution subtotal
CustomField.label: Federal Withholding Amount
